column16: Josh Harrison singles on a line drive to center fielder Rajai Davis.
Jayson Nix lines out to second baseman Ian Kinsler.
Travis Snider grounds out, second baseman Ian Kinsler to first baseman Victor Martinez.   Starling Marte to 3rd.
Ike Davis homers (8) on a fly ball to right field.
Russell Martin homers (6) on a fly ball to left field.
Gregory Polanco pops out to shortstop Eugenio Suarez.
